# API Server

## Structure
```
apps/api/
  prisma/schema.prisma
  src/routes/       # thin HTTP handlers
  src/services/     # business logic + prisma calls
  src/middleware/   # authenticate, requireRoles
  src/db/prisma.js  # PrismaClient singleton — always import from here
  src/plugins/      # error-handler
```

## Route pattern
```javascript
const schema = z.object({ nameEn: z.string().min(1) });
app.post('/api/v1/resource', async (request, reply) => {
  const parsed = schema.safeParse(request.body);
  if (!parsed.success) throw validationError('Invalid request', parsed.error.flatten());
  return reply.status(201).send(await myService.create(parsed.data));
});
```

## Auth
- Manager: `POST /api/v1/auth/login` → JWT (15m)
- Cashier: `POST /api/v1/auth/pin` + `X-Terminal-ID` + `X-Terminal-Secret`
- `await authenticate(request)` / `requireRoles('hub_manager')`

## Data access
- Prisma only — no raw `pg` pool
- Never return `passwordHash`, `pinHash`, `secretHash` in responses
- Health check may use `prisma.$queryRaw\`SELECT 1\``

## Errors
```json
{ "error": { "code": "INVALID_CREDENTIALS", "message": "...", "request_id": "uuid" } }
```
Use `src/utils/errors.js` + `@venue-pos/shared` error codes.

## Prefix
REST under `/api/v1/`. Health at `/health`.
